2017 Aon Featured Products & Practice Areas | Aon










WelcomeClientWorldAt the Convention CenterFeatured Products & Practice AreasAon PerspectivesAon at RIMSAon Agenda at RIMSRIMS Sessions Featuring AonSession SpeakersAon AttendeesMap of Aon HotelsPhiladelphia RestaurantsAon Colleague LoginActivate AccountMeetingsSchedule MeetingPowerful Perspective on 2017 Aon Focus Products
Aon Cyber Risk Solutions
Christian Hoffman provides an update on some of the notable events that took place within Aon's Cyber Risk Practice in 2016, including the acquisition of Stroz Friedberg and launch of the Aon's Cyber Captive Solution. As a result of these and other key milestones, Aon now offers a robust suite of solutions aimed at assessing and mitigating cyber exposures, and efficiently resolving them when they occur.

 

 

Aon Spectrum AnalyticsTM
Chris Iovino discusses an innovative new product offering that provides risk leaders with an interactive casualty claims dashboarding tool that leverages Aon Casualty Laser proprietary benchmarking data – with complementary leading advisory consultation – to identify cost savings opportunities and monitor the performance of pre-and post-loss casualty TCoR (Total Cost of Risk) mitigation strategies. Spectrum Analytics represents a new, interactive way of driving insight into casualty TCoR.

 

 

Aon Transaction Liability Solutions
Kyle Kalinch discusses the Aon's innovative approach to Transaction Liability Solutions, the types of coverages that a potential client might be seeking, and the role Risk Managers play in driving decision-making and ensuring optimal results. 

 

 
