Aon Benfield was named Best Global Reinsurance Broking Company for Analytics at Reactions Global Awards 2012[38]
Aon Hewitt was named Top Retirement Consultant of 2012 by PLANSPONSOR Magazine2[35][39]
Aon Hewitt was named Actuarial and Investment Consultant of the Year for 2012 at the Professional Pensions Awards[40]

